		<h1>
		
		
			Schizophrenics see through hollow-mask illusion
		
		</h1>
		<ul class="markerlist">
		<li>
		
		
			
				14:01 07 April 2009
			
			
		

		 by
			
				
					<a href="/search?rbauthors=Sandrine+Ceurstemont"><b>Sandrine Ceurstemont</b></a>
				
				
				
			
		
		</li>
		
		
			<li>
			For similar stories, visit the
				
					
						<a href="/topic/mental-health"><b>Mental Health</b></a>
					
					
					
					
				
					
					
						and <a href="/topic/brain"><b>The Human Brain</b></a>
					
					
					
						Topic Guides
					
				
